<font color="#FF0000">OPERATION CHICKEN CHASE SUCCES</font><br>
<tt>Sat Nov 22 16:12:47 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
I came by this morning, and all I could see was the bullet ridden body of the dog in the wire. Still hanging there in the wire, muscle spasms sometimes causing the lifeless body to twist.<br><br>
In December when we returned to the finger lake area we uncovered all the tunnel complexes the enemy had used to hide under. That's all that's left here, empty echoing, dirty, stinking dark tunnels. Not fit to even throw in a frag or smoke grenade to flush out the chickens. <br><br>
No need for a mop-up operation, only dead napalm smothering bodies left. <br><br>
Need to let the enemy, bury their own kind. <br><br>
Mustang Two Four, this is India 6.<br><br>
Mustang Two Four, this is India 6, come in.<br><br>
M Two Four,<br><br>
Operation has ended, repeat operation has ended.<br><br>
Operation a success enemy has been destroyed. Revealing communist documents captured. <br><br>
M Two Four, Request transportation out.<br><br>
SW, can’t think of any appropriate quote for this message.<br><br>
Perhaps I’ll quote that turn coat colonel here, but I think he meant for it to mean something else. <br><br>
&quot;About Face.&quot;<br>

